1 “SECTION 6. Section 5 of this 2026 Act is repealed on January 2, 2028.
2 “SECTION 7. This 2026 Act takes effect on the 91st day after the date on which the 2026
3 regular session of the Eighty-third Legislative Assembly adjourns sine die.”.
